 5. Плоский список из матрицы 
 [[1, 2], 
 [3, 4], 
 [5, 6]]
 matrix = [[1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6]]
 flat = [num for row in matrix for num in row]
 print(flat)
 6. Словарь: слово - длина слова ["apple", "banana", "kiwi"]
 words = ["apple", "banana", "kiwi"]
 word_lenghts = {word: len(word) for word in words}
 print(word_lenghts)

